Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.35,0:52:44.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.46,0:52:45.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,不客气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.91,0:53:08.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,纽约警局不知道到底发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}NYPD doesn't have a clue what was going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.51,0:53:11.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们甚至不知道这地方是谁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They don't even know who owns the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.71,0:53:14.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,那里之前全天候24小时都有门卫看守\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apparently there were guards on duty 24-7,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.99,0:53:17.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,但现在一个都不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but they can't find any of them--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.07,0:53:21.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,只能确认死者山姆·科尔比\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only the victims-- Sam Colby, Tracey Barberato--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.58,0:53:22.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,和特雷茜·巴伯拉多的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}have been ID'd.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.63,0:53:25.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,他们还收缴了还几百卷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They confiscated hundreds of digital files
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.66,0:53:28.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,从不同角度拍这个玻璃箱的录像\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}showing various angles of this glass box.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.38,0:53:33.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,曾经出现过一些模糊的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once in a while, they show some blurred shape pass through,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.49,0:53:35.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是只有几帧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but only a few frames.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.26,0:53:37.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,然后凶案发生当晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then on the night of the murders,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.39,0:53:40.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,录像中出现了这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}on camera, this appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.41,0:53:46.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.72,0:53:50.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,其他相机什么都没拍到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The other cameras saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.36,0:53:53.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,这个东西一动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And as soon as this thing moved,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.89,0:53:54.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,就消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.56,0:53:58.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,法医怎么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Forensics?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.70,0:54:00.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,尸体被残忍肢解了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The bodies were violently mutilated,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.47,0:54:02.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是没有留下任何指纹  DNA和纤维\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but no prints, no DNA, no fibers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.39,0:54:04.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,十分干净\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Completely clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.18,0:54:05.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没留下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.88,0:54:09.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,科尔局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Director Cole?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.17,0:54:11.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,有您的电话  是库柏打来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On your phone, it's Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.51,0:54:12.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.30,0:54:14.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,有您的电话  是库柏打来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On your phone, it's Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.15,0:54:17.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.95,0:54:30.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,我是科尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.22,0:54:33.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,好的  我等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I'll hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.53,0:54:35.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,-是他吗  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is it him? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.74,0:54:36.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,是他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.08,0:54:38.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我能听到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.76,0:54:40.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.64,0:54:42.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.66,0:54:45.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,你确定是他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you sure it's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.55,0:54:50.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,"麻烦"是什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you mean "Trouble"?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.11,0:54:55.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  我们明天早上第一件事就是去那\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, we'll be out there first thing tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.15,0:54:57.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,九点整安排一次会谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Set up an interview for nine o'clock sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.66,0:55:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,艾伯特  我们去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Albert, we're headed
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.59,0:55:04.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,南达科他州的黑丘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the Black Hills of South Dakota.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.85,0:55:06.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,黑丘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Black Hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.55,0:55:07.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.83,0:55:09.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这消息让我们很开心  艾伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As happy as this news makes us, Albert,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.89,0:55:11.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,但不能让别人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we can't put this on the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.42,0:55:13.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.71,0:55:15.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很想看看拉什莫尔山\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been dying to see Mount Rushmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.14,0:55:17.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想快点  这很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's good you want to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.70,0:55:18.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们天一亮就起飞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We fly at dawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.71,0:55:20.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,塔米  你和我们一起去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and, Tammy, you're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.45,0:55:31.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,存在的有着奇怪力量的荒诞的神秘事物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The absurd mystery of the strange forces of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.92,0:55:36.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,满满一卡车的安定怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How about a truckload full of Valium?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.19,0:55:45.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}枪炮酒吧
